alam ko

00:44:29.041 --> 00:44:32.044
kung gaano kadesperadong nais ng aking asawa
na magkaroon ng anak,

00:44:32.128 --> 00:44:33.796
kaya napahamak ako.

00:44:36.299 --> 00:44:37.383
Pero ang asawa ko…

00:44:40.511 --> 00:44:42.388
ay talagang mas kalmado kaysa sa akin.

00:44:43.347 --> 00:44:44.473
